name: autumn #4
description:
When you look at it from a distance, their beauty is indescribable. They provide it to passers-by at a cost.
The tree that is stripped is hit harder by the cold and wishes that the leaves had not left it and the clothes were warming and warming the tension.
The leaves die beautifully, but this is not the end of the tree, and after a hard and cold winter, new leaves will sprout on the tree and the tree will experience a fuller spring.
This my artwork of mine combines my photos and digital effects with aftereffects
